{"tid":1965057,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"仲有冇得戴口罩","createTime":"2020-04-09T08:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T08:52:30.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"17ce773d33fc286895e6a8b3c12fde30a131427e","tid":1965057,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T08:37:41.000Z","msg":"禁蒙面法上訴成功左"},{"pid":"13735ba02a733acef29651d7b11ff8734f0030c1","tid":1965057,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T08:42:39.000Z","msg":"仲有咁岩世衛又叫人唔駛戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n【口罩角色】世衛：研究後維持不建議在公眾場所戴口罩 防隱性病人保持距離勤洗手<br />\n<br />\n據最新指引，世衛建議患者才需要戴生口罩，並自我隔離及盡快尋求醫療協助，而照顧者與患者同處一室時，必須戴上口罩。<br />\n<br />\n美國疾病防治中心（CDC）的最新建議呼籲民眾，<strong>如在無法保持適當社交距離的公共場所</strong>，例如藥妝店及雜貨鋪，<strong>應戴上布面口罩</strong>，以防新冠肺炎傳染。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/28736/%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94-28738/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2%E3%80%91%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B%EF%BC%9A%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%BE%8C%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E5%A0%B4%E6%89%80%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E9%98%B2%E9%9A%B1%E6%80%A7%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E8%B7%9D%E9%9B%A2%E5%8B%A4%E6%B4%97%E6%89%8B?fbclid=IwAR12CbhHCC2IEnxFjD1pky_ZmAtXSPz-Is53zv5MD3uY9QgmbCiDIqnA560\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F28736%2F%25E6%2588%25B4%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594-28738%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%2589%25B2%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259B%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%258C%2581%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%2588%25B4%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E9%259